modName: Mage College Dorm Doors - Player Privacy
summary: Adds doors to every bedroom at the mages college.
descriptionHtml:
NOTE:  A similar mod has already been created by Mutak94.  I was not aware of this when I created the mod.  Please check out Mutak94\'s mod here...

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22289//?

This mod adds doors to every bedroom in the hall of attainment and the hall of countenance at the mage\'s college.  Now the students can have a bit of privacy!

The ownership of the chair in the player\'s room has been set to the player.  NPCs should no longer wander into your room to sit down.
author: Thicketford
